content.text: What is the stiffness matrix for this part of the groove structure?

The red circle highlights a section where the groove is vertical, resembling a transition into or out of a region. The stiffness is maximized along the Z-axis and minimized along the X- and Y-axes to prevent any potential damage to the groove.

### Stiffness Matrix
